node.accessibility_caption: Photo by chrissy teigen on September 11, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people sitting, people standing and indoor.

node.text: Seattle, Snohomish, Woodinville, we love you. It was so wonderful to head back to my childhood home - I got to cook in my old kitchen with the kindest current residents/now-family I could ever imagine! Seeing my old bedroom and the window I used to gaze out of, the road I used to bike up that i thought was soooo steep at the time and totally isn’t, was surreal. New snohomish, you’re so lucky for all the cute new stores on Main Street! WE had a fish market, a Piccadilly store and 25 antique shops. Now you have clothing, candles, gift shops and food!! and a fucking Starbucks in town!? Count your panther pride blessings!! At least your love of corn mazes hasn’t changed! Now onto bend, oregon followed by my mystery anniversary trip!
